1. Open Python Interactive Mode

In the terminal, type:

python3


You will see the interactive prompt: >>>.

2. Import the Requests library
>>> import requests

3. Access a website
>>> site = requests.get("http://google.com.br")

4. View page content
>>> site.content

5. View HTTP headers
>>> site.headers

6. Check response status
>>> site.status_code

7. Check the web server used by the site
>>> site.headers['Server']

8. Exit interactive mode
>>> exit()

